    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience that you can count on. It has been well-cared for and presents beautifully, making it a perfect choice for anyone looking for a high-quality, dependable car at a great value. Come see why this solid performer is the perfect addition to your driveway!",
