    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you can expect some minor oil leaks and a suspension that feels a bit loose. Cosmestically, the paint has some fading and there are several noticeable scratches and small dings around the body. The interior is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car who isn't concerned with perfection.",
